Revision history for Perl extension POD2::IT.

Legenda:
   + = new feature
   ! = updated feature/bug fix
   * = incompatible changes
   - = removed feature

0.07  
	! Updated perlboot.pod to 5.8.7 [osfameron]
	! Updated perlfunc.pod to 5.8.7 [dree]
	! Updated perlfaq[1..9] to 5.8.7 [dree]
	! Updated perlrequick to 5.8.7 [dree]
	! Added all nicknames contributors to Changes/README and so on [bepi]

0.06  Mon Jul 25 19:00:00 2005
	+ Added 'search_perlfunc_re' function to POD2::IT.pm in order
	  to use it with patched version of Pod::Perldoc. This allow
	  to use -f and -q perldoc switches [bepi]
	+ Added patches/ directory containing patches over Pod::Perldoc [bepi]

0.05  Sat Jul 23 16:00:00 2005
	+ First CPAN release  [bepi]

0.04  Wed Apr 17 16:00:00 2004
	+ perlfunc finished [dree]

0.02  Wed Jul 16 11:00:00 2003
	+ pod2it new Dump [bepi]

0.01  Thu Jun 19 01:29:11 2003
	+ original version; created by h2xs 1.21 with options
		-A -X -n POD2::IT by Enrico Sorcinelli <bepi@perl.it>
